                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-check mt-1 text-indigo-400"></i>
                            <span>You want flexibility to change styles easily.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-check mt-1 text-indigo-400"></i>
                            <span>You want to wash your bedding frequently (just wash the cover).</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-check mt-1 text-indigo-400"></i>
                            <span>You suffer from allergies and need regular cleaning.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <div class="bg-orange-50 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-orange-400">
                        <p class="text-xs text-orange-800 font-semibold uppercase mb-1">Key Drawback</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-orange-900">Requires assembly; the insert can sometimes bunch up inside
                            the cover.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

